==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Eventual
<hw>E*ven"tu*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧ventiel</ets>. See <er>Event</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Coming or happening as a consequence or result;
consequential.</def> <rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Final; ultimate.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Eventual</xex>
success.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Cooper.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Dependent on events;
contingent.</def> <rj><au>Marshall.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eventuality</ent>⟦br⟧
